= Haven

Haven is considered the capital city of Emergence (although politically this doesn’t grant it more benefits than other cities). It is the biggest city in Luminous territory and where culture and administration are centred. Haven is a coastal city with a cool maritime climate. It is the centre of the culture and administrative bodies of Luminous. Its architecture is characterised by the use of limestone and sandstone, alongside brighter colours and clean finishes.